-- Australia's Scentre debuts at A$3.21 after Westfield restructuring
-- 
-- Tue Jun 24, 2014 08:19PM EDT
-- None



SYDNEY, June 25 (Reuters) - Shares in shopping centre giant Westfield Group's <WDC.AX> <WRT.AX> new Australia and New Zealand company, Scentre Group Ltd <SCG.AX>, fell and those of its new U.S. and European arm Westfield Corp <WFD.AX> rose when the newly restructured firm relisted on Wednesday.

